APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW

2013-0109. State v. White.

Lucas App. No. L-10-1194, 2013-Ohio-51.

O’Connor, C.J., would accept the appeal on Proposition of Law Nos. I and IV only. Kennedy, J., would accept the appeal on Proposition of Law No. I only. French, J., would not accept Proposition of Law No. II.
